room_title: Escape room "The Last Hour of the Titanic" by Locked Room Omaha in Omaha
review: We did a team outing here and it was so much fun. We divided into two teams: Team Titanic and Team Fresh Meat. Both teams made it out with 7 and 3 minutes to spare. The Titanic room was well thought out and more difficult than other rooms Iâ€™ve done. I definitely recommend and would love to do the other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "The Last Hour of the Titanic" by Locked Room Omaha in Omaha
review: I love the Titanic Room. It was so much fun. Me and my hubby had a blast. Will be back to try another room soon.

room_title: Escape room "The Last Hour of the Titanic" by Locked Room Omaha in Omaha
review: Had a great time in the Titanic room! Friendly staff and challenging (but not frustratingly so) puzzles to solve. Will be going back!

room_title: Escape room "The Last Hour of the Titanic" by Locked Room Omaha in Omaha
review: We LOVED our experience in the Last Hour of the Titanic! It was our first ever escape room! The staff was super friendly and we made it through in the last minute (perfect amount of difficulty!).

room_title: Escape room "The Last Hour of the Titanic" by Locked Room Omaha in Omaha
review: My oldest son was home for college this week, and this was top on our list of things to do! We chose the Titanic room, and were so excited to go. You are never sure if something will live up to your expectations... Locked Room Omaha did! There were 4 of us (3 teens and myself), and it was so much fun to do this together! Can't wait to try another room!
